  "keyFeatures": [
    "Write Markdown and JSX seamlessly in the same document",
    "Add custom nestable components with a commands (/) menu",
    "Apply text marks (bold, italic, strikethrough, code, tooltips) with a marks menu",
    "Automatic theme detection with light/dark mode support",
    "Built on ProseMirror for robust document editing",
    "Rich component library (callouts, code snippets, accordions, tabs, steps, cards, mermaid diagrams)",
    "Fully customizable and extensible architecture",
    "TypeScript support with complete type definitions"
